    <entry>
      <title>【算法】快速排序</title>
      <link href="/2024/07/02/%E3%80%90%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E3%80%91%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F/"/>
      <url>/2024/07/02/%E3%80%90%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E3%80%91%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>C++代码</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> MAXSIZE = <span class="number">1e5</span> + <span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> num[MAXSIZE];</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">quick_Sort</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> num[], <span class="type">int</span> l, <span class="type">int</span> r)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(l &gt;= r) <span class="keyword">return</span> ;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> std = num[(l + r) &gt;&gt; <span class="number">1</span>], i = l, j = r;<span class="comment">// 这里圆括号可以去掉，优先级：位移运算符 &lt; 算数运算符</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(i &lt;= j) &#123;     </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span>(num[j] &gt; std) j--;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span>(num[i] &lt; std) i++;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(i &lt;= j) <span class="built_in">swap</span>(num[i++], num[j--]);            <span class="comment">// 相等的时候也交换是为了i++，j--</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 此时j &lt; i</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">quick_Sort</span>(num, l, j);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">quick_Sort</span>(num, i, r);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> n;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, &amp;n);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) <span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d&quot;</span>, &amp;num[i]);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">quick_Sort</span>(num, <span class="number">0</span>, n - <span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d &quot;</span>, num[i]);</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> 算法 </tag>
            
            <tag> 排序 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>【从零开发操作系统】1.搭建学习环境</title>
      <link href="/2024/07/02/%E3%80%90%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%911-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/"/>
      <url>/2024/07/02/%E3%80%90%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%B6%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E3%80%911-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="一、配置学习环境"><a href="#一、配置学习环境" class="headerlink" title="一、配置学习环境"></a>一、配置学习环境</h1><hr><ol><li><p>安装Oracle Virtual Box</p></li><li><p>准备NASM环境</p></li><li><p>cmd执行diskpart</p> <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">DISKPART&gt; </span><span class="language-bash">create vdisk file=path\dingst.vhd maximum=10 <span class="built_in">type</span>=fixed</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 这一步创建了大小为10m的固定类型虚拟磁盘文件，文件名为dingst.vhd</p></li><li><p>编写hello.asm文件</p> <figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">org 07c00h</span><br><span class="line">mov ax, cs</span><br><span class="line">mov ds, ax</span><br><span class="line">mov es, ax</span><br><span class="line">call Disp</span><br><span class="line">jmp $</span><br><span class="line">Disp:</span><br><span class="line">    mov ax, BootMsg</span><br><span class="line">    mov bp, ax</span><br><span class="line">    mov cx, 16</span><br><span class="line">    mov ax, 01301h</span><br><span class="line">    mov bx, 000ch</span><br><span class="line">    mov dl, 0</span><br><span class="line">    int 10h</span><br><span class="line">BootMsg: db &quot;Hello, OS World!&quot;</span><br><span class="line">times 510 - ($-$$) db 0</span><br><span class="line">dw 0xaa55</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>切换到NASM环境所在目录下cmd执行<code>nasm path\hello.asm -o bootDINGST.bin</code>编译hello.asm</p></li><li><p><code>dd if=bootDINGST.bin of=path\dingst.vhd bs=512 count=1</code>将汇编生成二进制文件写入虚拟磁盘文件中</p><p> （此时文件目录如图<img src="https://img.picui.cn/free/2024/06/28/667ebda99b483.png" alt="1.1.png"></p></li><li><p>virtualbox新建虚拟电脑</p><ol><li>类型和版本都选Other或者Other&#x2F;Unknown</li><li>内存大小默认64MB即可</li><li>虚拟硬盘选项选择已有虚拟硬盘，找到一开始创建的dingst.vhd</li><li>选择完毕后创建即可</li></ol></li><li><p>开机，看到如下画面即配置完毕</p><p> <img src="https://img.picui.cn/free/2024/06/28/667ebda99c787.png" alt="1.2.png"></p><hr></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> 自制 </tag>
            
            <tag> 操作系统 </tag>
            
            <tag> tutorial </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>【保姆级】一篇文章搞定Github + Hexo搭建个人博客</title>
      <link href="/2024/06/30/%E3%80%90%E4%BF%9D%E5%A7%86%E7%BA%A7%E3%80%91%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%90%9E%E5%AE%9AGithub%20+%20Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
      <url>/2024/06/30/%E3%80%90%E4%BF%9D%E5%A7%86%E7%BA%A7%E3%80%91%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%90%9E%E5%AE%9AGithub%20+%20Hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol><li><p>安装Node.js和git（这一步参考其他任意教程即可，都配置好后再做下一步</p><p> 可以通过cmd运行以下3条命令检验是否配置成功</p> <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">git -v</span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 若都显示对应的版本号就ok</p></li><li><p>安装Hexo，命令行执行<code>npm install hexo-cli -g</code>即可</p></li><li><p>新建用于存放博客文件的文件夹blog</p></li><li><p>在blog中右键打开git bash然后依次执行<code>hexo init</code>和<code>npm install</code> (下载慢可以更改npm源)</p><p> 此时文件目录如图<img src="https://img.picui.cn/free/2024/06/30/6680eea788cd9.png" alt="1.1.png"></p></li><li><p>执行<code>hexo server</code>（可简写为<code>hexo s</code>)在本地开启博客服务</p><p> （这个命令也可用于以后先在本地查看修改的效果，而不是直接上传到github</p></li><li><p>然后浏览器访问localhost:4000看到如图所示即成功<img src="https://img.picui.cn/free/2024/06/30/6680eea7a390b.png" alt="1.2.png"></p></li><li><p>更换主题</p><ol><li>找到喜欢的hexo主题并下载比如主题名为”theme_name”</li><li>复制到blog&#x2F;themes目录下</li><li>更改blog&#x2F;_config.yml里的theme的值为刚才复制的博客主题的文件夹名”theme_name”，比如我这里是butterfly<img src="https://img.picui.cn/free/2024/07/01/66826372f3cea.png" alt="1.3.png"></li><li><code>hexo s</code>启动服务，再次访问localhost:4000，不出意外的话就能看到更换主题后的博客主页啦！（否则请参考对应主题的文档，看比如是否有主题依赖的插件需要额外安装（比如butterfly主题就需要再执行<code>npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save</code>来安装相关渲染插件</li></ol></li><li><p>部署到github</p><ol><li><p>配置git</p><ol><li><p>打开git bash</p></li><li><p>执行以下2行命令</p><p> username就改为自己的昵称，<a href="mailto:&#x66;&#x6f;&#x6f;&#x40;&#98;&#97;&#x72;&#46;&#x63;&#x6f;&#109;">&#x66;&#x6f;&#x6f;&#x40;&#98;&#97;&#x72;&#46;&#x63;&#x6f;&#109;</a>改为自己的邮箱</p> <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;username&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;foo@bar.com&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 最后执行</p> <figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global --list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 能看到刚才配置的信息就ok</p></li></ol></li><li><p>添加SSH密钥</p><ol><li>git bash中运行<code>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;配置git时填的邮箱&quot;</code>然后无脑回车</li><li>打开github在设置页找到SSH and GPG keys</li><li>点击New SSH key</li><li>标题随便起（方便自己区分就行</li><li>Key type默认Authentication Key即可</li><li>在C盘:\用户\用户名\目录下可以找到.ssh的文件夹，打开id_rsa.pub，全选复制粘贴到key那一栏后Add SSH key</li><li>然后执行<code>ssh -T git@github.com</code>（这一步如果有提示询问是否继续链接输入yes就ok </li><li>出现successfully内容代表成功</li></ol></li><li><p>在github创建名为“你的github用户名.github.io”的公开仓库</p></li><li><p>配置部署相关内容</p><ol><li><p>复制SSH的<a href="mailto:&#x67;&#x69;&#116;&#64;&#x67;&#x69;&#116;&#104;&#117;&#98;&#46;&#99;&#x6f;&#109;">&#x67;&#x69;&#116;&#64;&#x67;&#x69;&#116;&#104;&#117;&#98;&#46;&#99;&#x6f;&#109;</a>:username&#x2F;username.github.io.git一栏内容</p><p> （我这里的username是我的github账号名XTERNALXLUE</p></li><li><p>打开blog&#x2F;_config.yml配置deploy字段如图<img src="https://img.picui.cn/free/2024/07/01/6682630e80502.png" alt="1.4.png"></p><p> (注意这里改了branch为main，github建库时可能默认为master，也要做相应修改)</p></li><li><p>在blog文件夹打开gitbash执行<code>npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</code></p></li><li><p>再执行<code>hexo g -d</code>将本地博客文件上传到github仓库中</p><p> （如果之后对配置进行修改后同步到github上不生效，执行<code>hexo clean</code>后在尝试同步)</p></li></ol></li><li><p>最后访问“你的github用户名.github.io”这个网址（不出意外的话）就可以看到自己的博客啦！</p></li></ol></li><li><p>写文章</p><ol><li><p>blog文件夹打开git bash执行<code>hexo new &quot;title&quot;</code>（可简写为hexo n “title”)</p></li><li><p>文章路径在blog&#x2F;_source&#x2F;_posts目录下</p></li><li><p>打开文件以markdown语法编写即可</p></li><li><p>如果是把已经写好的.md文件放到这里，记得在文章开头补上</p> <figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: &#x27;title&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">date: </span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">tags: </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>写好后在git bash执行<code>hexo g -d</code>即可同步至博客</p></li></ol><hr></li><li><p>补充</p><p>剩下的就是对博客主题相关的配置设定了</p><p>不同主题对应的设置也不一样</p><p>所以这一部分请参考<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/">Hexo中文文档</a>和对应主题的官方文档</p></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      
